      "Text": "Security update for spice",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "Spice was updated to fix three security issues.\n    \nThe following vulnerabilities were fixed:  \n* CVE-2015-3247: heap corruption in the spice server (bsc#944460)\n* CVE-2015-5261: Guest could have accessed host memory using crafted images (bsc#948976)\n* CVE-2015-5260: Insufficient validation of surface_id parameter could have caused a crash (bsc#944460)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
